   377вҶ’## Caveats
   382вҶ’By default, `input-otp` handles password managers for you.
   383вҶ’The password manager badges should be automatically shifted to the right side.
   384вҶ’
   385вҶ’However, if you still want to block password managers, please disable the `pushPasswordManagerStrategy` and then manually block each PWM.
   386вҶ’
   387вҶ’```diff
   388вҶ’<OTPInput
   389вҶ’  // First, disable library's built-in strategy
